# Build outputs and local cruft — keep images small and reproducible.
# apps/ and packages/ ARE included: the image's web stage builds the operator
# console (SPA) from the pnpm workspace. Their generated dirs stay excluded via
# the **/ patterns above; only source + manifests enter the context.
**/bin
**/obj
**/target
**/node_modules
**/dist
# TS incremental state — must not leak in, or `tsc -b` skips emitting dist/.
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.git
.github
*.md
crates
tests
fixtures
drivers
